Dialogue: 0,1:52:04.15,1:52:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,life.\NAll right? So let's say you're seeking
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.36,1:52:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightenment or at least an advanced\Nstate of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:52:11.44,1:52:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and there isn't any this is no good and\Nthis is uh all good.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.23,1:52:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The process the process may take you all\Naround the world may teach may take you
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.92,1:52:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to uh see and hear certain teachers may\Ntake you to great cathedrals may require
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.00,1:52:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,sacrifice walking barefoot across the\Ndesert whatever
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.48,1:52:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told this joke before. This guy's\Nvery uh enthused about religion. And so
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.52,1:52:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,he visits the Holy Land and uh he sees\Nthis fisherman out there and he says,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.71,1:52:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"Uh,\Nhello."
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.59,1:52:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And the fisherman looks over at him. He\Nsays, "What do you want?" She face.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.52,1:53:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told that joke before, but it's\Nbecause of uh our uh we are enamored of
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.08,1:53:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the glamour of religiosity.\NWe oursel become glamorized by it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.23,1:53:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhhuh.\NBe pleased with the direction you're
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.52,1:53:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,going and not just a goal.\NThe practical reality versus fantasy and
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.36,1:53:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the glamour of success.\NSuccess is an inner is an inner
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.96,1:53:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,condition.\NSuccess is an inner condition. What the
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.92,1:53:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,world calls success may have little or\Nnothing to do with what you consider it
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.76,1:53:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to be. And vice versa. You may consider\Nwhat you have is successful and the
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.23,1:53:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,world completely ignores it and\Nconsiders that it's nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.36,1:53:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Choose and make decisions instead of\Njust hoping.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.44,1:53:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hope to go to college.\NBust your chops until you get there and
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.15,1:54:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,bust your chops to do the best while\Nyou're there.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:02.63,1:54:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So just hoping it is not enough. You\Nhave to back it up with effort. Okay,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.96,1:54:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the next one.\N>> What?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.63,1:54:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,>> We're breaking for lunch.\N>> We're breaking for what?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.36,1:54:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Lunch.\N>> Lunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.48,1:54:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,>> These people want to eat on top of\Neverything else.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.48,1:54:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good God. Okay,\Nwe'll see you again at what time?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.67,1:54:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Um,\N>> what?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.63,1:54:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,>> What time?\N>> Two o'clock.
